'''Firefox OS'''，由[[Mozilla基金會|Mozilla基金會]]主導研發的[[開放原始碼|開放原始碼]][[行動作業系統|行動作業系統]]，採用[[Linux核心|Linux核心]]。這個計劃於2011年7月25日宣布<ref name="m.d.p announce">{{cite mailing list |last = Gal |first = Andreas |title = Booting to the web |mailinglist = mozilla.dev.platform |date = June 25, 2011 |url = http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.platform/browse_thread/thread/7668a9d46a43e482?pli=1 |accessdate = November 20, 2011 |archive-date = 2013-05-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510191212/http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.platform/browse_thread/thread/7668a9d46a43e482?pli=1 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，一開始主要應用於[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]和[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]<ref name="MDN">{{cite web|url=https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox_OS|title=Firefox OS|accessdate=September 17, 2012|date=August 21, 2012|publisher=Mozilla|archive-date=2015-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204175623/https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox_OS|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但因難以打入手機市場，2016年7月已停止推出預載Firefox OS的新手機，轉型主打[[物联网|物聯網]]的作業系統。

類似於[[Google_Chrome_OS|Google Chrome OS]]，它是一種{{link-en|網絡作業環境|Web desktop}}，以[[Gecko|Gecko]]瀏覽器引擎為中心，采用[[HTML5|HTML5]]來開發。它允許基於HTML5的應用程式，能透過[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]語言，直接透過裝置硬體來做相互溝通<ref>{{cite web |url=https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/WebAPI |title=WebAPI - MDN |publisher=developer.mozilla.org |date=2014-01-27 |accessdate=2015-02-01 |archive-date=2014-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225123535/https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/WebAPI |dead-url=no }}</ref>。所有應用都基於網路，希望使用者一開機就能夠连接上[[網際網路|網際網路]]，但仍可透過{{link-en|HTML5 cache Manifest|Cache manifest in HTML5}}或相關[[API|API]]在離線時使用。

==發展目標==
2011年7月25日，[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla公司]]開始Firefox OS的研發，目標在於建立一個獨立且完整的作業系統，用以推動網路開放，並使開發人員能夠在不同手機平台上開發[[跨平台|跨平台]]應用程式。並確立了一些工作方向：建立新的WebAPI來驅動裝置和作業系統的功能，例如：電話和相機；建立權限模型來保證系統的安全，以及底層驅動[[Android|Android]]設備的低階程式碼<ref name="m.d.p announce">{{cite mailing list |last = Gal |first = Andreas |title = Booting to the web |mailinglist = mozilla.dev.platform |date = June 25, 2011 |url = http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.platform/browse_thread/thread/7668a9d46a43e482?pli=1 |accessdate = November 20, 2011 }}</ref>。2012年正式發布了Firefox OS。

Mozilla研發總監[[安德里亞斯·加爾|安德里亞斯·加爾]]（Andreas Gal）形容目前已存在的行動裝置平台猶如「[[封閉平臺|圍牆花園]]」<ref name="knowyourmobile">{{cite web |url = http://www.knowyourmobile.com/features/1267951/mozillas_boot_2_gecko_and_why_it_could_change_the_world.html |title = Mozilla’s Boot 2 Gecko and why it could change the world - Features |publisher = Know Your Mobile |date = March 2, 2012 |accessdate = August 18, 2012 |archive-date = 2013-01-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130128021225/http://www.knowyourmobile.com/features/1267951/mozillas_boot_2_gecko_and_why_it_could_change_the_world.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，Firefox OS將完全使用開放的HTML5[[網頁標準|網頁標準]]技術，不涉及專利軟體及技術。Firefox OS希望建立起一個平台，讓符合網頁標準的網頁瀏覽器便能夠執行軟體，讓程式開發者統一在同一套標準下開發可以共通使用的應用程式，不需再為各平台各別開發專用的應用程式。

==發展歷史==
2011年7月25日，Mozilla研發總監安德里亞斯·加爾（Andreas Gal）於討論群組上宣佈「Boot to Gecko」專案（簡稱''B2G''）<ref name="m.d.p announce">{{cite mailing list |last = Gal |first = Andreas |title = Booting to the web |mailinglist = mozilla.dev.platform |date = June 25, 2011 |url = http://groups.google.com/group/mozilla.dev.platform/browse_thread/thread/7668a9d46a43e482?pli=1 |accessdate = November 20, 2011 }}</ref>。這項-{zh-hans:信息; zh-tw:消息}-引發了許多科技媒體關注<ref name="androidesque1">{{cite web |url = http://gagagadget.com/wordpress/2011/07/firefox-phone-mozilla-os-mobile/ |title = The Firefox Phone? Mozilla Working on Android-Esque OS |work = blog |publisher = Gagagadget |date = July 26, 2011 |accessdate = August 4, 2011 |archive-date = 2014-07-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140727081600/http://gagagadget.com/wordpress/2011/07/firefox-phone-mozilla-os-mobile/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="androidesque2">{{cite web |url = http://androinica.com/2011/07/mozilla-borrows-from-android-to-create-its-own-mobile-operating-system/ |title = Mozilla borrows from Android to create its own mobile operating system |work = blog |publisher = androinica |author = Andrew Kameka |date = July 26, 2011 |accessdate = August 4, 2011 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110830130454/http://androinica.com/2011/07/mozilla-borrows-from-android-to-create-its-own-mobile-operating-system/ |archive-date = 2011-08-30 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。其中根據[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]引述：“Mozilla表示，B2G基於標準的開放網路有潛力成為一個具有競爭力的替代品，取代由主流行動作業系統提供的現有單一供應商應用程式開發環境。”<ref name="androidesque3">{{cite web |url= http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2011/07/mozilla-eyes-mobile-os-landscape-with-new-boot-to-gecko-project.ars |title= Mozilla eyes mobile OS landscape with new Boot to Gecko project |publisher= [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |date= July 26, 2011 |author= Ryan Paul |accessdate= August 4, 2011 |archive-date= 2011-09-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110912005225/http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2011/07/mozilla-eyes-mobile-os-landscape-with-new-boot-to-gecko-project.ars |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2012年2月28日，在執行於Android型號的智慧型手機上，首次公開展示Firefox OS<ref name="pcworld1">{{cite web |url = http://www.pcworld.com/article/250879/first_look_at_mozillas_web_platform_for_phones_boot_to_gecko.html |title = First Look at Mozilla's Web Platform for Phones: 'Boot to Gecko' |author = Ginny Maies |date = 2012-02-28 |publisher = PCWorld]] |accessdate = 2012-03-23 |archive-date = 2012-04-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402210600/http://www.pcworld.com/article/250879/first_look_at_mozillas_web_platform_for_phones_boot_to_gecko.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="HSW">{{cite web |url = http://hoowstuffworks.blogspot.com/2011/07/mozilla-making-mobile-os-using-android.html |title = Mozilla making mobile OS using Android |work = blog |date = July 2011 |publisher = I Didn't Know That! |accessdate = 2011-08-04 |archive-date = 2013-07-22 |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6IJCwKRoL?url=http://hoowstuffworks.blogspot.com/2011/07/mozilla-making-mobile-os-using-android.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。7月2日，Boot to Gecko正式被命名為Firefox OS<ref>{{cite web |last = Brown |first = Mark |url = http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-07/03/mozilla-firefox-os |title = Mozilla's HTML5 phone platform now called Firefox OS, launching 2013 (Wired UK) |publisher = Wired.co.uk |date = August 8, 2012 |accessdate = August 18, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120814133035/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-07/03/mozilla-firefox-os |archivedate = 2012年8月14日 }}</ref>，並於8月展示部份系統截圖<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2196370/mozilla-shows-off-firefox-os-screenshots |title = Mozilla shows off Firefox OS screenshots |publisher = The Inquirer |date =  |accessdate = August 18, 2012 |archive-date = 2013-10-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023163156/http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2196370/mozilla-shows-off-firefox-os-screenshots |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2012年9月2日，Strategy Analytics分析師預測，Firefox OS將在2013年占據1%的智慧型手機市場<ref>{{cite web |url = http://blogs.strategyanalytics.com/WSS/post/2012/09/27/Firefox-OS-to-Capture-1-Percent-Share-of-Global-Smartphone-Market-in-2013.aspx |title = Firefox OS to Capture 1 Percent Share of Global Smartphone Market in 2013 |publisher = Strategy Analytics |date =  |accessdate = September 27, 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024000503/http://blogs.strategyanalytics.com/WSS/post/2012/09/27/Firefox-OS-to-Capture-1-Percent-Share-of-Global-Smartphone-Market-in-2013.aspx |archivedate = 2012年10月24日 }}</ref>。

2013年1月10日，[[中興通訊|中興通訊]]於[[國際消費電子展|國際消費電子展]]上證實將推出Firefox OS智慧型手機<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.techweekeurope.co.uk/news/zte-firefox-os-smartphone-ces-103878 |title=CES 2013: ZTE Firefox OS Smartphone Coming In 2013 | TechWeekEurope UK |publisher=Techweekeurope.co.uk |date=January 10, 2013 |accessdate=February 26, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118075045/http://www.techweekeurope.co.uk/news/zte-firefox-os-smartphone-ces-103878 |archive-date=2013-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並在2013年7月2日，[[西班牙電信|西班牙電信]]推出首款商用Firefox OS手機[[ZTE_Open|ZTE Open]]<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.techstake.org/2013/07/telefonica-launches-first-firefox-os-phones-in-spain.html |title= Telefonica launches First Ever Firefox OS-based Phone in Spain |author= Aditya Dey |publisher= TechStake |accessdate= July 2013 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130707091153/http://www.techstake.org/2013/07/telefonica-launches-first-firefox-os-phones-in-spain.html |archive-date= 2013-07-07 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。西班牙GeeksPhone公司接著也推出[[Geeksphone_Keon|GeeksPhone Keon]]和[[Geeksphone_Peak|Peak]]。2月24日，Firefox OS商業計劃正式擴大<ref>{{cite web |url = https://blog.mozilla.org/press/2013/02/firefox-os-expansion/ |title = Mozilla Announces Global Expansion for Firefox OS |publisher = mozilla |date = February 24, 2013 |accessdate = March 27, 2013 |archive-date = 2013-12-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213070101/https://blog.mozilla.org/press/2013/02/firefox-os-expansion/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。Mozilla於[[巴塞羅那|巴塞羅那]][[世界行動通訊大會|世界行動通訊大會]]記者會上宣佈，第一波Firefox OS手機將提供給[[巴西|巴西]]、[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[蒙特尼哥羅|蒙特尼哥羅]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]、[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]與[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]]的消費者；[[LG集團|LG集團]]、[[中興通訊|中興通訊]]、[[華為|華為]]和[[TCL集團|TCL集團]]將承諾生產Firefox OS設備<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-21522713 |title = Mozilla reveals Firefox smartphone launch partners |publisher = BBC |date = February 24, 2013 |accessdate = March 28, 2013 |archive-date = 2013-05-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130527131024/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-21522713 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2013年5月27日，[[鴻海科技|鴻海科技]]與Mozilla簽署合作協議，合作範圍包括平板電腦和其他手持裝置產品<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.techbang.com/posts/13532-hon-hai-announced-that-will-be-developed-in-collaboration-with-mozilla-firefox-os-environment |title = Firefox OS 平板現身！鴻海宣布將與 Mozilla 合作開發 Firefox OS 生態環境 |publisher = T客邦 |date = 2013-06-03 |accessdate = 2016-04-02 |archive-date = 2016-04-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425214210/http://www.techbang.com/posts/13532-hon-hai-announced-that-will-be-developed-in-collaboration-with-mozilla-firefox-os-environment |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年5月14日，Mozilla基金會和T2Mobile合作推出Firefox OS參考平台手機被名為“Flame”，這是專為開發人員用於開發和測試的手機<ref>{{cite web|url=https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Firefox_OS/Developer_phone_guide/Flame|title=Flame|work=Mozilla Developer Network|publisher=Mozilla|accessdate=August 31, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906094403/https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Firefox_OS/Developer_phone_guide/Flame|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

截至2014年12月16日，Firefox OS手機在全球共有14家營運商和近28個國家上市<ref name="countries">{{Cite web |url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/12/16/firefox-os-expands-to-nearly-30-countries/ |title=Firefox OS Expands to Nearly 30 Countries |date=December 16, 2014 |publisher=[[Mozilla_Corporation|Mozilla Corporation]] |accessdate=2014-12-23 |archive-date=2014-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218130507/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2014/12/16/firefox-os-expands-to-nearly-30-countries/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年12月8日，Mozilla聯網裝置部門副總Ari Jaaksi在其[[Twitter|Twitter]]頁面宣佈將終止Firefox OS智慧型手機的開發與銷售，而將Firefox OS聚焦在[[物联网|物聯網]]的發展<ref>{{cite news|url=http://udn.com/news/story/7098/1366216-%E6%9B%B4%E8%91%97%E9%87%8D%E7%89%A9%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2-Mozilla%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95Firefox-OS%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F|title=更著重物聯網 Mozilla終止發展Firefox OS手機|publisher=聯合新聞網|date=2015-12-09|accessdate=2015-12-09|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215002952/http://udn.com/news/story/7098/1366216-%E6%9B%B4%E8%91%97%E9%87%8D%E7%89%A9%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2-Mozilla%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95Firefox-OS%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年2月，Mozilla公司在寄送給開發者的電子郵件中宣布：在2.6版本發佈後，他們將停止開發手機平台上的Firefox OS，原開發團隊將會移到別的專案上，例如Firefox TV和其他的智慧家電。

2016年9月27日，Mozilla宣布Firefox OS於手機平台的商業性開發已經停止，且所有相關的程式碼將從mozilla核心中移除，以便未來Gecko（Firefox的排版引擎）的開發不受已停止的手機專案之影響。但也會釋出Firefox OS 2.6版穩定的原始碼，供[[开源软件|開源軟體]]社群繼續利用與開發手機作業系統。只是因為此後的Gecko引擎在演進中將逐漸與2.6版為止的Firefox OS越來越不相關，這意味著[[开源软件|開源軟體]]社群必須自行跟上Gecko的發展來修改B2G程式碼，對社群成員將是一大挑戰。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/mozilla.dev.fxos/FoAwifahNPY/Lppm0VHVBAAJ|title=B2G OS and Gecko Annoucement from Ari Jaaksi & David Bryant|accessdate=2016-09-27|date=2016-09-27|archive-date=2011-01-22|archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20110122130054/https://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/mozilla.dev.fxos/FoAwifahNPY/Lppm0VHVBAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref> 目前（2016-10-26）在Firefox OS官網上，看到的下載仍是2.5版開發者預覽版。

雖然手機上的Firefox OS停止開發了，但給物聯網的專案仍繼續，例如Firefox OS TV。

